														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1286340">
									

<p>Right, so I've been asked to give an explanation for this page.</p>
<p>Basically, when trying to come up with my own <a href="/scp-001">SCP-001</a> proposal a while back, I read everyone else's. Didn't want to copy or steal accidentally, so I review and made myself some notes. And then I happened to think for a bit&#8230; &quot;What if this one is right? How would that change things?&quot; Which inevitably led me down a &quot;Oh, holy shit&quot; trail into this project. One story for each proposal, with each one going horribly awry in some way or imparting some of my personal thoughts/feelings on the object. This is my homage to you 001 authors. Excellent work, all of you. :)</p>
<p>Enjoy!</p>

							</div>

